title: Street Challenge Extreme Velocity
description: Street Challenge Extreme Velocity is the most realistic and fast paced online drag racing game in the internet.  It encompasses timing, ratio making, with the fun of racing people from around the world in real time racing combat.  SC EV gives you the choice of racing in tornaments, head to head, or bracket racing.  SC EV also allows you to chat with people from around the world in real time chat, or you can post comments in the forum. Come join us today and test your racing skills against the best online racers in the world
